column44:
From July 1, 2018, all submitted reports of clinical trials must
contain a data sharing statement, to be included at the end of the
manuscript. Data sharing statements must indicate...Whether additional, related documents will be available (eg, study protocol, statistical analysis plan, informed consent form);

